name: Mad Moxxi
description: I painted Alice (IG: @aliceinanutshell) using Cameleon COlors and WolfeFX bodypaints. She posed with a tinsel spool as a hat, and I fixed it in Photoshop. I paint her a lot and she's always hitting me up with these crazy character ideas. I don't even play the game, but this one sounded fun. Trying out a multiple edition on this one, minting 5 on HicEtNunc. Other work and links by me are at www.LarsPeterson.com
